EcosystemFragment
Presents a user interface comprising menu items in the action bar (and the overflow menu), as well as a display of the terrain of the ecosystem simulation (implemented by TerrainView) and additional key measures of the simulation.

Manages and choreographs creation of, and subsequent operations performed on (and results returned from) a simulation involving an instance of Ecosystem.
